definitions.definition: To offer (oneself or someone else) for sexual activity in exchange for money .
To sacrifice (oneself, one's talents etc.) in return for profit or other advantage; to exploit for base purposes.

main_definition: ( transitive , reflexive ) To offer (oneself or someone else) for sexual activity in exchange for money . [from 16th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( transitive , derogatory ) To sacrifice (oneself, one's talents etc.) in return for profit or other advantage; to exploit for base purposes.
